{
  "stem": "24364.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember that as a smaller child, I wasn't allowed to do any work on Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I was allowed to write in school-- we went to school on Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But at home wasn't allowed to sew, I wasn't allowed to write.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But as time went on, this also ceased.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I wasn't allowed to go swimming on Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But once I met my father in the street carrying his swimming trunks, so that ceased too.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went to temple on the high holidays mainly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think-- I don't think we went-- not only on high holidays.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We also went on the like, Pesach, and so on, but that was about it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was not too much religion going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had a kosher household though.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But, [LAUGHS] it's really funny.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was also sort of lax.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My-- since my mother felt that the children should have certain things because they are good for them, so we had ham, for instance.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the ham, in order for the fleishig plate not to get treif, so it was eaten on milchig plate.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I still remember that, it's so funny.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or when we had salami, which we had sometimes, so we couldn't put it on butter.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to have it on a piece of paper, and the bread and butter on the plate.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it had to be eaten sort of like this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Everybody laughs about it when I recall those things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my father-- my father traveled quite a bit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- we also had wholesale paper.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so he was selling in the neighborhood villages.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my grandmother worked in the store.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother worked sort of part time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She did some bookkeeping.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And part time, I don't know what she did.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
